00:49:17.840 --> 00:49:20.880
The engineers and the
highly educated workforce

00:49:20.880 --> 00:49:24.180
team up and are working the
thing out together, right?

00:49:24.180 --> 00:49:25.830
That happens less
than the US system.

00:49:25.830 --> 00:49:29.220
So this kind of
integration of the design

00:49:29.220 --> 00:49:31.020
team and the production
team is something

